	<h3 class="title"><a href="/279813#comment-3017159" class="active">All the serious preppers I</a></h3>
    <div class="submitted active">Submitted by <a href="/user/772" title="View user profile.">BobW</a> on Thu, 03/28/2013 - 13:53.  <a class="permalink" href="/comment/3017159">Permalink</a></div>
